{"word":"κίδναμαι","slug":"κίδναμαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κίδναμαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>. = <el>σκεδάννυμαι</el>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a>, only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><i>to be spread abroad</i> or <i>over</i>, of the dawning day, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>ὕπνος ἐπ' ὄσσοις κ.</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}